This paper discusses trajectory following in robotics, which falls under the category of robotics and control (cs.RO). The paper also discusses reinforcement learning and optimal control algorithms, which are subfields of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of a simulator for evaluation suggests that the paper may also fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper mentions a 2D dynamics and kinematics simulator, which suggests that computer vision (cs.CV) may also be relevant.
